-- AVI of South Africa Says Per-Share Earnings Increased Between 30% And 40%
-- B y   N a s r e e n   S e r i a
-- 2010-12-15T07:32:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-15/avi-of-south-africa-says-per-share-earnings-increased-between-30-and-40-.html
AVI Ltd. said per-share earnings for
its continuing operations, including capital gains and losses on
the disposal of assets, are expected to rise by between 30
percent and 40 percent in the six months through Dec. 31 from a
year ago.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
